Class CopyController

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.GenericController
      • control.CopyController

  • public class CopyController
extends GenericController
    CopyController is controls copying a photo from one album into another, while keeping it in the album it is currently in
    Author:
    Niles Ball, Scott Lahart
